Setup

Using R version 4.5.0 (2025-04-11) , tidyverse version 2.0.0, and isoorbi version 1.4.1.1.

# load packages
library(isoorbi) # for orbitrap function
library(dplyr) # for mutating data frames
library(stringr) # for extarcting text information
library(forcats) # for recoding factors
library(ggplot2) # for data visualization
library(cowplot) # arrange multipanel plots

Data

# isotopocules data
data <- 
  "data/replicates" |>
  orbi_find_isox() |>
  orbi_read_isox() |>
  orbi_flag_satellite_peaks() |> 
  orbi_flag_weak_isotopocules(min_percent = 30) |> 
  # very tight agc data, discard anything that's 5% above or below the mean
  orbi_flag_outliers(agc_fold_cutoff = 1.05) |>
  # pull out replicate from filename
  mutate(
    replicate = str_extract(filename, "Replicate_\\d") |> str_replace("_", " ")
  ) |>
  # expand amino acid names
  mutate(
    compound = compound |>
      fct_recode(
        "Alanine" = "Ala_imm",
        "Arginine" = "Arg_imm",
        "Methionine" = "Met_imm",
        "Phenylalanine" = "Phe_imm"
      )
  )

average number of ions tic * it.ms in the Orbitrap analyzer, in 5 data groups

# calculate ratios for 13C/M0
ratios <- data |>
  orbi_define_basepeak("M0") |>
  orbi_filter_isox(isotopocules = "13C") |>
  group_by(replicate) |>
  orbi_summarize_results(ratio_method = "sum") 
✔ [121ms] orbi_define_basepeak() set M0 as the ratio denominator and calculated
18031 ratios for 5 isotopocules/base peak (15N, 13C, 2H, 33S, and 34S)

✔ [2ms] orbi_filter_isox() filtered the dataset by isotopocules (13C) and
removed a total of 12003/18031 rows (66.6%)

✔ [40ms] orbi_summarize_results() summarized ratios from 4588 peaks (excluding
1440 flagged peaks; excluding 0 unused peaks) using the sum method and grouping
the data by replicate, filename, compound, basepeak, and isotopocule

Figure 11 top panel

p_top <- data |>
  orbi_plot_raw_data(
    isotopocules = "M0",
    x_breaks = c(5, 10),
    y = intensity,
    y_scale = "log",
    color = compound,
    show_outliers = FALSE
  ) +
  facet_wrap(~replicate, nrow = 1) +
  labs(x = "time / min", y = "EIC / arb. unit") +
  theme(strip.text = element_text(size = 16))
p_top

Figure 11 bottom panel

p_bottom <- 
  ratios |>
  ggplot() +
  aes(
    replicate, ratio, color = compound, shape = compound,
    ymin = ratio - ratio_sem, ymax = ratio + ratio_sem
  ) +
  # standard deviations
  geom_rect(
    data = function(df) 
      df |> group_by(compound) |>
      summarize(ratio_mean = mean(ratio), ratio_sd = sd(ratio)),
    map = aes(
      ymin = ratio_mean - ratio_sd, ymax = ratio_mean + ratio_sd,
      x = NULL, y = NULL, xmin = -Inf, xmax = +Inf, color = NULL),
    fill = "gray90", show.legend = FALSE
  ) +
  # averages
  geom_hline(
    data = function(df) 
      df |> group_by(compound) |>
      summarize(ratio_mean = mean(ratio)),
    map = aes(yintercept = ratio_mean, color = compound),
    show.legend = FALSE
  ) +
  # data points
  geom_errorbar(width = 0.1, show.legend = FALSE) + 
  geom_point(fill = "white", size = 3) +
  facet_grid(compound ~ ., scales = "free_y") +
  # scales
  scale_color_brewer(palette = "Dark2") +
  scale_shape_manual(values = c(21:25)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = scales::pretty_breaks(3)) +
  # labels
  labs(x = NULL, color = NULL, shape = NULL,
       y = expression("ratio ("^13*C/M0*")")) +
  # theme
  theme_bw() +
  theme(
    text = element_text(size = 16),
    panel.grid = element_blank(),
    strip.background = element_blank(),
    strip.text = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks.x = element_blank(),
    legend.position = "top"
  )
p_bottom

Figure 11 combined

plot_grid(
  p_top + theme(legend.position = "none"), p_bottom,
  ncol = 1, rel_heights = c(1, 2), align = "v", axis = "lr"
)

# Setup

# Data

```{r}
# isotopocules data
data <- 
  "data/replicates" |>
  orbi_find_isox() |>
  orbi_read_isox() |>
  orbi_flag_satellite_peaks() |> 
  orbi_flag_weak_isotopocules(min_percent = 30) |> 
  # very tight agc data, discard anything that's 5% above or below the mean
  orbi_flag_outliers(agc_fold_cutoff = 1.05) |>
  # pull out replicate from filename
  mutate(
    replicate = str_extract(filename, "Replicate_\\d") |> str_replace("_", " ")
  ) |>
  # expand amino acid names
  mutate(
    compound = compound |>
      fct_recode(
        "Alanine" = "Ala_imm",
        "Arginine" = "Arg_imm",
        "Methionine" = "Met_imm",
        "Phenylalanine" = "Phe_imm"
      )
  )

# calculate ratios for 13C/M0
ratios <- data |>
  orbi_define_basepeak("M0") |>
  orbi_filter_isox(isotopocules = "13C") |>
  group_by(replicate) |>
  orbi_summarize_results(ratio_method = "sum")
```

```{r}
p_bottom <- 
  ratios |>

    fill = "gray90", show.legend = FALSE
  ) +
  # averages
  geom_hline(
    data = function(df) 
      df |> group_by(compound) |>
```
